  <text type="edition" xml:lang="si-Latn-t-si-Sinh">
    <body>
      <lg xml:lang="sa">
        <l>[yasya jñānadayāsindhor agādhasyānaghā guṇāḥ |</l>
        <l>sevyatām akṣayo dhīrāḥ sa śriye cāmṛtāya ca ||]</l>
      </lg>
    <p xml:id="AKS0.1">he dhīrāḥ (yuṣmābhiḥ) akṣayaḥ saḥ śriye ca amṛtāya ca sevyatām, yanū mehi kriyākāraka padasambandhayi; pan̆ḍitavariṇi topavisin kṣayabhāva yakaṭa noyannāvū hētemē trivargasampat piṇisat nivan piṇisat sevinā læbēvā yanu artthayi.</p>
    <p xml:id="AKS0.2">agādhasya pātālatala rahitahō itāgæmburu; jñānadayāsindhoḥ, næṇa kuḷuṇu sayuru bandu; yasya, yam utumekugē; guṇāḥ, prajñā kṛpādiguṇayō; anaghāḥ, pav rahitahō nirdoṣada; akṣayaḥ saḥ, nirvvikāravū hētema; śriye ca, trivargasampat piṇisada; amṛtāya ca, nivan piṇisada; dhīrāḥ, pan̆ḍitavariṇi topavisin; sevyatām, sevunā læbēvā.</p>
    <p xml:id="AKS0.3">mē ślokaya budun·gē nairggika guṇānusmaraṇayen buddhasēvāva karaṇulæbēvayi yana abhiprāyen kiyana ladæyi mē nāmaliṅgānuśāsanayehi artthakiyana væḍitara ācārīn·gē sammatayi ― brahmaviṣṇumaheśādi sevā kiyanaladæyi samahara ācārīn·gē matayi ― bhaṭṭojidīkṣitācāryyātmaja bhānudīkṣitācārīn visin gurusevā dakvana bavak mut buddhasēvā noveyi amarācārīn saugatavīmehi hetunætæyi dæḍisē kiyati — mema ācārīn·gē druṣṭivirodhaheyin kiyana pamaṇak vinā bhāratītomō gurusevā artthaya sphuṭa nokarannīya — maheśvara nam ācārīn visin viracitavū amarakoṣa viveka nam vyākhyānayehi mē buddhādi kisivek nodakvā ślokārttha pamaṇak kiyati.</p>
  <head type="sub">purātana sannaya.</head>
    <p xml:id="AKS1.0.1-1">śāstrārambhayehi sarvajñayanṭa pūjāvidhānakaḷa kalhi parahitānuśāsanayen vighnopaśamaya karannāvū puṇyasampattiya ræskarannō; “yasyajñānadayāsindhoḥ” yanādī mē solōvak dækvūhu ― jñāna, samastavastuviṣayavū parijñānayenhā; dayā, duḥkhayen samuddharaṇavāñjā lakṣaṇavū karuṇāyen; sindhoḥ, sāgarayakvænivū nohot uktalakṣaṇavū jñānadayādedenāṭa vipulādhāraheyin sāgarayakvænivū; agādhasya, anut visin pātālatala nodaknālada jñānadayādedenāgē keḷavara ætiheyin pirisin̆dagata nohækkāvū gāmbhīryya æti; yasya, yam sarvvajñayak·hugē; guṇāḥ, maitrīkṣamopaśamādī guṇayō; anaghāḥ, rāgādidoṣarahitayō da; he dhīrāḥ, pan̆ḍitavariṇi; akṣayaḥ, parama karuṇādī guṇaśālitvayen parahita sukhasampādanayehilā kṣayaknættāvū hevat virāmayak nættāvū nohot saṃsārayen sundarasthānayaṭa giyabava hetukoṭageṇa ajarāmaraheyin kṣayak nættāvū saḥ, ē sarvvajñatema; śriye ca, trivargasampattiya piṇisada; amṛtāya ca, nivan piṇisada; sevyatām, topavisin sevinā læbēvā.</p>
    <p xml:id="AKS1.0.1-2">mē solōva sarvajñayan·gē sāgaratvayen rūpaṇayaheyin sarvajñayanṭahā sāgarayaṭa śleṣayi; mehi samudrayāgē agādhatva nam pātālatalaya nodækkahæki bavaya; anaghavū guṇayō nam ratnākaratvādīhuya; akṣayatva nam paripūrṇabavaya; śrī nam śrīdevatāya amṛta nam amāyayi datayutu “yasya jñānadayāsindhoḥ” yanādiyen iṣṭadevatāśrīrvādadækvūhu “śriye ca amṛtāya ca” yannen sakalajñānapravṛttiya phalapramāṇaheyin pravṛttiphala dækvūhu.</p>
    <p xml:id="AKS1.0.1-3">mē solōvehi śleṣayen tamankaraṇa śāstra yāgēda svarūpa kīha hēmesē datayutu ෴ jñānadayā, kavitvavaktṛtvādiyehihō aṣṭādaśa vidyāsthānayehi jñānadānasampattiya hetukoṭa geṇa; sindhoḥ, sāgarayakvænivū; agādhasya, anantaroktavū guṇayogaya hetukoṭa geṇa patulnodækkahækkāvū; yasya, yam śāstrayak·hugē, guṇāḥ, laghutvaviṣpaṣṭatvādiguṇayō; anaghāḥ, śubhahetuhuda; he dhīrāḥ; pan̆ḍitavariṇi; akṣayaḥ, sampūrṇavū; saḥ, ē jñānadayāsindhuvatemē hevat mē nāmaliṅgānuśāsanayatema; śriye ca, trivargasampattiya piṇisada nohot vāṅmaya śilpa dænīmalakṣaṇakoṭa æti svārtthasampattiya taddhetukatrivarggahetuvū parārtthasampattīya yana mē svārtthasampat parārtthasampat deka piṇisada; amṛtāya ca, ē svārtthasampattiyenudu puṇyajñānasambhārayen ayatnayen siddhavannāvū mokṣaya piṇisada; sevyatām, śruticintāvyākhyānādilakṣaṇavū sēvāva karaṇu læbēvā.
  </p>
    <p xml:id="AKS1.0.1-4">mē śāstrapakṣayehi dānan dāḥ yana vākyayehi ḍudāñ dāne yana dhātuhu keren (sampadādibhyaḥ) kvip ca yi kvip kaḷa kalhi dā kiyā tibeyi jñānasya dāḥ tasyā ī lakṣmī jñānadeyi vākyageṇa ṣaṣṭhīsamāsakoṭa jñānade śabdaya siddhakalhi ohukeren tṛtīyā kaḷakala jñānadayā yi kiyā rūpayaveyi datayutuyi.
  </p>
    </body>
